article.headline: Dion Brown scores 25 points and UMBC wins 92-87 against Lehigh
article.description: — Dion Brown had 25 points in UMBC's 92-87 win against Lehigh on Saturday.
article.linkText: Dion Brown scores 25 points and UMBC wins 92-87 against Lehigh
article.story: BALTIMORE -- — Dion Brown had 25 points in UMBC's 92-87 win against Lehigh on Saturday. Brown also added eight rebounds for the Retrievers (5-5). Bryce Johnson scored 24 points and added five assists and three steals. Marcus Banks had 13 points. Tyler Whitney-Sidney finished with 24 points and seven rebounds for the Mountain Hawks (1-7). Bube Momah added 18 points, seven rebounds and two steals and Keith Higgins Jr. finished with 18 points and three steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
